@node "About" "About TMD"



@{i}@{u}About TMD@{ui}@{uu}


Basicaly this program is a nice looking (well I think so anyway :) clock
program that requires very little memory and system resources (see @{"bugs" link "Bugs" 0}). The
memory readout is almost in real time so it beats the Workbench title bar to
the punch.


                                                            @{"BackĀToĀMain" link "Main" 0}
@endnode

